## ðŸ› ï¸ Available Supabase Features

### Database Operations
```typescript
// Query data
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('table_name')
  .select('*')
  .eq('column', 'value')

// Insert data
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('table_name')
  .insert([{ column: 'value' }])

// Update data
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('table_name')
  .update({ column: 'new_value' })
  .eq('id', 1)

// Delete data
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('table_name')
  .delete()
  .eq('id', 1)
```

### Real-time Subscriptions
```typescript
// Subscribe to table changes
const subscription = supabase
  .channel('table_changes')
  .on('postgres_changes', 
    { event: '*', schema: 'public', table: 'table_name' },
    (payload) => {
      console.log('Change received!', payload)
    }
  )
  .subscribe()
```

### Authentication
```typescript
